<p>BPC-157 and GHK-Cu both appear in conversations about healing and recovery, but they are not interchangeable. They come from different sources, act through different pathways, and shine in completely different use cases.</p>

<p>This comparison breaks down the research behind each peptide so you can think clearly about which one (or both) might be relevant to your goals. If you are making decisions that affect your health, involve a licensed healthcare provider.</p>

