<!-- ========== QUICK TAKE ========== -->
<hr class="sep">
<h2>Quick Take: What Each Peptide Does Best</h2>

<p>The simplest way to think about this comparison: BPC-157 is most often discussed for internal tissue repair, especially in the gut and connective tissue. GHK-Cu is most often discussed for external tissue quality, especially skin, hair, and wound appearance.</p>

<table class="tbl">
